            <h3>Design</h3>
            <p class="project-font-grey">To ensure the project was suitably themed and had the look and feel of an ABC kids app, I was given access to a large range of artwork created by ABC kids. To reinforce the flashcards concept I designed a card packet for each category. I decided to theme each category with one particular ABC brand. For example the category ‘Numbers’ has been themed with Giggle and Hoot characters and artwork. The actual flashcard and their flipping animation was created using SCSS, with the relevant image and text placed within.</p>
