              <h3 class="text-color">Navigation</h3>
              <p class="project-font-white">Another high priority of this project was to keep the navigation structure as simple as possible, to ensure ease of use for all age groups. This was partly achieved with large, bright and often animated buttons.</p>

              <p class="project-font-white">The categories page has a simple easy to use layout, allowing the user the swipe left or right to view more categories. The layout of this page was important to not overwhelm the user with too many choices, but still make it intuitive that more categories are available. As the user flips each flashcard, audio is played to engage the user and reinforce the pronunciation of each word. After all items in a category are shown the user is directed to a small animated game. This has been done to reward the user for completion and to give them encouragement to try another category.</p>
